          "description": "This unit's attacks will not wake sleeping enemies.\n\nUntil the end of this unit's third turn while on the battlefield:\n- This unit is immune to Poison and Sleep status effects.\n- This unit is immune to Stun effects unless it is burning.\n- Unless it is burning, this unit has 80% damage reduction and has a 100% chance to survive any damage that would defeat it with 1HP.\n\nUntil the end of this unit's second turn while on the battlefield, each time this unit takes damage from an attack, a random non-burning enemy is immediately granted Cursed Sleep for 200TU, then a random non-burning enemy immediately becomes Lethal Poisoned for 999TU. This is not a Skin passive skill."
